Slide the cupcake clip into a side section of hair to keep strays from scattering, blend watermelon, ice cream, and cherries together in a tasty mixed up trio, or add a shiny pineapple to your bangs to keep you looking neat and sweet. Durable metal clips bend easily to open and snap securely around hair for lasting hold and scrumptious styling!

fields.name: Scunci Scrunchies 25ct

With 25 soft neutral tones in the collection, it’s easy to take an everyday 'do and transform it into a gorgeous, statement-making style by adding a touch of color. Each scrunchie is made with a durable elastic core encased in loose folds of soft cotton fabric that keeps hairstyles firmly in place and protects against damage and tangles. Make maintaining a neat and refined look effortless with natural color accessories that complement every hair color, type, and texture. About scünci hair accessories: When it comes to keeping your look on trend, scünci has you covered with today’s hottest hair accessories, including stylish headbands, super-comfy scrunchies, glitzy bobby pins, glam barrettes, and much more. From work to workouts to nights out, scünci lets you express your personal style and gets you ready for any occasion. Take control of your hair and look amazing whatever you do and wherever you go. Whether bling is your thing or casual is your calling, with scünci, ü got this.
